To Make A Note Or A Command In Lua, We Use:
-- or --[[ ]]

- Example:
local x = "Hello World" -- declare a local value
print(x)
===> Output: "Hello World"

local y = "Hello World" --[[
This Is A Comment Which You Can Break The Lines
Like This
Until You Close The Bracket
]]
print(y)
===> Output: Hello World
